#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.empty_like.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.empty\\_like"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:1 of
msgid "Return a new tensor with the same shape and type as a given tensor."
msgstr "返回一个与给定 tensor 具有相同形状和类型的新的 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:3 of
msgid ""
"The shape and data-type of `a` define these same attributes of the "
"returned tensor."
msgstr "`a` 的形状和数据类型定义了所返回 tensor 的这些属性。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:6 of
msgid "Overrides the data type of the result."
msgstr "覆盖结果的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:8 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, None as default"
msgstr "如果为 True 则将 tensor 分配在 GPU 上，默认为 None"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:10 of
msgid ""
"Overrides the memory layout of the result. 'C' means C-order, 'F' means "
"F-order, 'A' means 'F' if ``prototype`` is Fortran contiguous, 'C' "
"otherwise. 'K' means match the layout of ``prototype`` as closely as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"覆盖结果的内存布局。'C' 表示 C 顺序，'F' 表示 Fortran 顺序，如果 ``"
"prototype`` 是 Fortran 连续的则 'A' 表示 'F'，否则表示 'C'。'K' 表示"
"尽可能匹配 ``prototype`` 的布局。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:16 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Array of uninitialized (arbitrary) data with the same shape "
"and type as `a`."
msgstr "**out** -- 一个与 `a` 具有相同形状和类型的未初始化（任意）数据的数组。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:22 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ones_like`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:23 of
msgid "Return a tensor of ones with shape and type of input."
msgstr "返回一个与输入具有相同形状和类型的全一 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`zeros_like`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:26 of
msgid "Return a tensor of zeros with shape and type of input."
msgstr "返回一个与输入具有相同形状和类型的全零 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`empty`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:29 of
msgid "Return a new uninitialized tensor."
msgstr "返回一个新的未初始化的 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ones`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:32 of
msgid "Return a new tensor setting values to one."
msgstr "返回一个将值设为一的新 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`zeros`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:35 of
msgid "Return a new tensor setting values to zero."
msgstr "返回一个将值设为零的新 tensor。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:38 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.empty.empty_like:39 of
msgid ""
"This function does *not* initialize the returned tensor; to do that use "
"`zeros_like` or `ones_like` instead.  It may be marginally faster than "
"the functions that do set the array values."
msgstr ""
"此函数*不会*初始化返回的 tensor；如果需要初始化，请使用 `zeros_like` 或 `"
"ones_like` 代替。它可能比那些设置数组值的函数略微快一些。"

